reviewText: Night of the Fools is funny and sad and gives a different slant to PLAN 9 FROM OUTER SPACE.  I especially like the actor who plays Bela Lugosi.  Film quality could be better, but I never get tired of watching this movie.
This was a fun, cheap, entertaining little movie made the way i like it, bad but i a fun way. Would recommend it to all Ed Wood fans or fans of low budget movies.
